        Material Non-Disclosure When Selling Queensland Property: What Sellers Must Understand
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        Queensland sellers have a legal obligation to disclose facts that would influence a buyer's decision. Here's what that means in practice and how to protect yourself.
      </p>
